==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[twelve]]-[[tone]] [[technique]]'''

# A system of musical composition devised by [[w:Arnold Schoenberg|Arnold Schoenberg]], as a method of composing with twelve notes which are related solely to each other.

